                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Elbaz, Y. & Schuldiner, M.</span>: <span class="ti">Staying in touch: the molecular era of organelle contact sites.</span> <span class='so'>Trends Biochem. Sci., 36, 616-623 (2011)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21958688" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Stefan, C. J., Manford, A. G. & Emr, S. D.</span>: <span class="ti">ER-PM connections: sites of information transfer and inter-organelle communication.</span> <span class='so'>Curr. Opin. Cell Biol., 25, 434-442 (2013)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23522446" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Porter, K. R. & Palade, G. E.</span>: <span class="ti">Studies on the endoplasmic reticulum. III. Its form and distribution in striated muscle cells.</span> <span class='so'>J. Biophys. Biochem. Cytol., 3, 269-300 (1957)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/13438910" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Rosenbluth, J.</span>: <span class="ti">Subsurface cisterns and their relationship to the neuronal plasma membrane.</span> <span class='so'>J. Cell Biol., 13, 405-421 (1962)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14493991" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Endo, M.</span>: <span class="ti">Calcium-induced calcium release in skeletal muscle.</span> <span class='so'>Physiol. Rev., 89, 1153-1176 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19789379" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Hogan, P. G., Lewis, R. S. & Rao, A.</span>: <span class="ti">Molecular basis of calcium signaling in lymphocytes: STIM and ORAI.</span> <span class='so'>Annu. Rev. Immunol., 28, 491-533 (2010)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20307213" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R7"><span class='au'>Carrasco, S. & Meyer, T.</span>: <span class="ti">STIM proteins and the endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane junctions.</span> <span class='so'>Annu. Rev. Biochem., 80, 973-1000 (2011)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21548779" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R8"><span class='au'>West, M., Zurek, N., Hoenger, A. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">A 3D analysis of yeast ER structure reveals how ER domains are organized by membrane curvature.</span> <span class='so'>J. Cell Biol., 193, 333-346 (2011)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21502358" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R9"><span class='au'>Manford, A. G., Stefan, C. J., Yuan, H. L. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">ER-to-plasma membrane tethering proteins regulate cell signaling and ER morphology.</span> <span class='so'>Dev. Cell, 23, 1129-1140 (2012)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/23237950" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R10"><span class='au'>Min, S. W., Chang, W. P. & Sudhof, T. C.</span>: <span class="ti">E-Syts, a family of membranous Ca<sup>2+</sup>-sensor proteins with multiple C2 domains.</span> <span class='so'>Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA, 104, 3823-3828 (2007)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/17360437" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R11"><span class='au'>Sudhof, T. C.</span>: <span class="ti">Calcium control of neurotransmitter release.</span> <span class='so'>Cold Spring Harb. Perspect. Biol., 4, a011353 (2012)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/22068972" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R12"><span class='au'>Rizo, J. & Sudhof, T. C.</span>: <span class="ti">C2-domains, structure and function of a universal Ca<sup>2+</sup>-binding domain.</span> <span class='so'>J. Biol. Chem., 273, 15879-15882 (1998)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9632630" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R13"><span class='au'>Idevall-Hagren, O., Dickson, E. J., Hille, B. et al